Janky Promoters Tallahassee with @karlousm & @chicobean The 85 South Show booked a show with Janky Promoters down in Tallahassee, Florida and this what happened. The venue didn't have the money agreed to, the green room was in the women's bathroom and a camera man had a seizure but The 85 South Show goes on and Karlous and Chico roasted the hell out of the entire night.
